node.text: The next time your workout partner suggests that y’all should skip leg day.. throw a plate at their head 🤷‍♀️

What’s that one saying? Never trust a woman who trains legs for fun? 😂 😈

Outfit from @noireblanc.ca ❤️‍🔥

node.text:
Squat Programming Available NOW‼️

👉Link in bio!👈 I have carefully designed 3 levels of programming to get you stronger. EVERYTHING that I did are in these programs. Never before seen! Each program is only $29.99 AND that comes with direct access to me if you have any questions along the way or need help while you run these. I will personally respond.

🏋️‍♂️Level 1: 5 week building program. VOLUME! 3x a week frequency. Back squats. Build muscle and work on technique. Accessory work focused on hamstrings.

🏋️‍♂️Level 2: 8 week building program. 2x a week frequency. Adding in front squats with back squats. You will be alternating between heavier and lighter weeks. Accessory work to strengthen weaknesses.

🏋️‍♂️Level 3: 6 week peaking program. 3x a week frequency. Front and back squats. Accessory work to strengthen weaknesses. Higher %

I’ll be responding to all program related DMs and comments! LFG!!!!🔥🤘😈

SQUATS‼️*read caption*

OF COURSE I’ll be squatting heavy again and then some! I LOVE it. Aside from my downtime, I change the way that I train from time to time so that I can work towards new goals and change my physique, give body a break, etc. I go through different phases because I love that I can do it all!! I’ve competed in the IFBB, I’ve been insanely shredded, I’ve also been very strong and thicc. I love it all. This is my LIFE.

Out of everything that I’ve accomplished, I fell most in love with squatting heavy weights.💯 There’s something about throwing plates onto a barbell, getting underneath it and feeling that sick adrenaline rush🔥 There is no better therapy in my opinion. Being strong is fucking awesome. 🤘

How did I do it⁉️Programming. I cannot stress this enough. Following the right program will take your lifts to the next level. I did a lot of crazy programs for fun with my amazing workout partner (yes, for fun) like Smolov, GVT and a whole lot of YOLO lifts for the gram.. but when I decided to lift smarter, I got MUCH stronger.

Guys, I carefully created 3 levels of squat programming for YOU. If you want to take your squat to the next level, I’ll be releasing my never before seen programming tomorrow at 12:00 est. EVERYTHING that I did will be in the programs. Everything. There will be 3 different phases/levels. I can’t wait to talk more about this tomorrow.
